PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781384336
OL,3,COxford Union to host Tommy Robinson
OL,4,Cfor debate despite outcry
OL,6,FSpeakers include Robinson, whose real
OL,7,Fname is Stephen Yaxley-Lennon,
OL,8,Falongside fellow far-right voice
OL,9,FLaurence Fox, opposed by others
OL,10,Fincluding former Tory MP Jacob Rees-
OL,11,FMogg.
OL,13,FIt was reported last month that the
OL,14,Fdebate had been delayed after
OL,15,Fsignificant outcry about Yaxley-
OL,16,FLennon's attendance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
