PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781384336
OL,3,COxford Union to host Tommy Robinson
OL,4,Cfor debate despite outcry
OL,6,FThe most significant opposition then
OL,7,Fcame from faith leaders including the
OL,8,FBishop of Oxford Steven Croft and
OL,9,Ffounder of the Oxford Foundation Imam
OL,10,FMonawar Hussain, who said they were
OL,11,F"disturbed and saddened" when he was
OL,12,Finvited to speak.
OL,14,FIan McKendrick, vice chairman of
OL,15,FOxford Stand Up To Racism, has accused
OL,16,FYaxley-Lennon of inciting "violent
OL,17,Frace riots" in Southampton, Belfast
OL,18,Fand Glasgow over the past two weeks.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@XO]xD@[OUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
