OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781384336
OL,3,COxford Union to host Tommy Robinson
OL,4,Cfor debate despite outcry
OL,6,FDr Darja Wischerath, from the
OL,7,FUniversity of Bath's institute of
OL,8,Fdigital security and behaviour (IDSB),
OL,9,Fwas the author of a study which
OL,10,Fanalysed the impact of Yaxley-Lennon's
OL,11,Fpublic Telegram channel on rioting in
OL,12,Fthe summer of 2024.
OL,14,FHe told the Press Association: "They
OL,15,Fnever say explicitly, you may now go
OL,16,Fout and riot, but what they do is kind
OL,17,Fof dehumanise and delegitimise other
OL,18,Fgroups so that violence against them
OL,19,Fcan become legitimate."
OL,26,@vD@`OU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
