PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781384336
OL,3,COxford Union to host Tommy Robinson
OL,4,Cfor debate despite outcry
OL,6,FOxford East MP Anneliese Dodds has
OL,7,Fsaid that Yaxley-Lennon "has no place"
OL,8,Fin Oxford and accused the union of
OL,9,Fproviding a "loudspeaker" to the far
OL,10,Fright.
OL,12,F"It is particularly frustrating to see
OL,13,Fthis event still going ahead, despite
OL,14,Fthe union society being well aware of
OL,15,Fthe extent of local concern about it,"
OL,16,Fsaid Ms Dodds.
OL,18,FThe Oxford Union's social media shows
OL,19,Fthat a motion from a member to direct
OL,20,Fthe president to disinvite Yaxley-
OL,21,FLennon from attending failed last week.
OL,26,@oD@YOUoD@fO]qD@MOUqD@YO]tD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
