PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781384336
OL,3,COxford Union to host Tommy Robinson
OL,4,Cfor debate despite outcry
OL,6,FThe motion argued that the debate
OL,7,F"will serve as a rally for Tommy
OL,8,FRobinson" and was not conducive to the
OL,9,F"future safety of free speech".
OL,11,FIn a statement in the same post on
OL,12,FInstagram, the OU president Arwa
OL,13,FElrayess said that she was "very much
OL,14,Flooking forward" to the debate, where
OL,15,Fmembers would have a chance to
OL,16,F"challenge those speakers".
OL,18,FThe Oxford Union has been contacted
OL,19,Ffor comment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@IO]qD@AOUqD@^O]uD@\OUvD@PO]xD@
